examples.en: She is treasurer of the college.
She reaffirmed that she would serve as treasurer.
Who's running for treasurer this year?
She has been designated to take over the position of treasurer.
Anyone wishing to apply for a grant should write to the Treasurer.
The treasurer gave a brief overview of the financial consequences.
It's ironic that the weakest student in mathematics was elected class treasurer.
The town treasurer has been linked to the kickback scheme and other financial malefactions.
Mr Leesom proposed Mrs Banks for the position of Treasurer (=he suggested formally that she should be the treasurer).
